    "en": {
      "title": "Controversial Chinese ship at Hambantota port",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "China's Yuan Wong-5 surveillance ship, which recently caused controversy, arrived at Hambantota port today (16) morning.",
        "Earlier, the ship was scheduled to anchor at Hambantota port on August 11 and stay till August 17.",
        "However, the arrival of the ship was delayed due to the subsequent controversy.",
        "In this situation, the Ministry of External Affairs has issued a statement that the said vessel has been given permission to enter the Hambantota port during the period from today 16th to the upcoming 22nd."
      ],
